data.description: BUY THIS AWESOME HOME FOR $2,450 DOWN AND LESS THAN $1,300 PER MONTH OR TRADE! PERFECT MOVE-IN CONDITION AND READY FOR YOU.  THIS SPACIOUS TOWNHOUSE PRESENTS A GREAT OPPORTUNITY FOR FIRST-TIME HOME BUYERS OR YOUNG FAMILIES LOOKING FOR A PRACTICAL, LOW-MAINTENANCE LIFESTYLE. THE PROPERTY IS READY TO WELCOME YOU WITH ITS GREAT CONDITION AND DESIRABLE FEATURES AS WELL AS RECENTLY UPDATED ESSENTIALS. IT IS SET ON A QUIET COMPLEX IN EASTWOOD CLOSE TO THE POPULAR YARD 56 SHOPPING CENTER, JOHNS HOPKINS BAYVIEW MEDICAL CENTER, SCHOOLS, AND DOWNTOWN BALTIMORE. ITS LOCATION PROVIDES EASY ACCESS TO PUBLIC TRANSPORTATION FACILITIES AND MAJOR COMMUTING ROUTES INCLUDING I-95, MAKING IT A PERFECT CHOICE FOR THOSE SEEKING CONVENIENCE AND COMFORT.  BOTH JASPIAN PARK AND HARBOR VIEW PARK ARE A SHORT WALKING DISTANCE AWAY AND OFFER A WEEKEND ESCAPE FOR TIME TO ENJOY THE OUTDOORS INCLUDING BASEBALL DIAMONDS AND MULTI-PURPOSE COURTS AT HARBOR VIEW PARK. THERE IS PLENTY OF SAFE SIDEWALK SPACE FOR CASUAL STROLLS WITH THE FAMILY PET OR FOR MORE INTENSE EXERCISE TO UNWIND AFTER A LONG DAY AT WORK. THERE IS A COMMUNITY GREEN SPACE WITH A PLAYGROUND AT THE OTHER END OF THE STREET WHICH HAS PLENTY OF OPEN SPACE FOR WALKING THE FAMILY PET IN A BEAUTIFUL, TREE-LINED ENVIRONMENT. YOUR KIDS CAN ALSO ENJOY THE PLAYGROUND AREA WHILE YOU RELAX ON THE BENCH UNDER SHADE TREES. AS YOU APPROACH THE PROPERTY, YOU'LL BE GREETED BY A CHARMING PORCH, PERFECT FOR ENJOYING A MORNING COFFEE OR AFTERNOON BREEZES. STEP INSIDE AND BE CAPTIVATED BY THE OPEN LIVING SPACE THAT SEAMLESSLY TRANSITIONS TO THE DINING AREA AND KITCHEN. ASCEND TO THE UPPER LEVEL AND YOU'LL DISCOVER TRANQUIL BEDROOMS WITH CEILING FANS AND A TIDY, FULLY-TILED BATHROOM. THE FINISHED LOWER LEVEL IS ENHANCED BY THE LARGE WINDOWS THAT INVITE ABUNDANT NATURAL LIGHT. IT CAN BE USED FOR A SPACIOUS THIRD BEDROOM, CONVENIENT HOME OFFICE, OR ENJOYABLE HOBBY SPACE. THE REAR OF THE BASEMENT HOUSES THE LAUNDRY ROOM, UTILITY ROOM, AND WORKSHOP THAT LEADS OUT TO THE PRIVATE YARD. DON'T MISS OUT ON THIS INCREDIBLE OPPORTUNITY!  OPEN HOUSE EVERY DAY - CALL FOR TIMES!
